49
00:05:36.627 --> 00:05:37.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Calmarse?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:05:38.046 --> 00:05:40.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿No ves el peligro que nos rodea?</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:05:41.883 --> 00:05:46.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
