<c.bg_transparent>- Así es.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:35.264 --> 00:08:38.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y debemos entregar algo valioso.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:38.476 --> 00:08:41.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se desatará una guerra jamás vista,</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:41.187 --> 00:08:43.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>a menos que llevemos el dragón</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con su mamá.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:48.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero Zym es muy pequeño.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:48.528 --> 00:08:50.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debe aprender a volar.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:51.197 --> 00:08:54.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pareces tener</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una conexión especial con él.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:55.159 --> 00:08:57.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás puedes enseñarle.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:57.245 --> 00:08:59.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Yo? Podría intentarlo.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:59.497 --> 00:09:02.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo quería aprender</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un poco de magia de luna.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:09:04.418 --> 00:09:06.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te enseñaré algunas cosas.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:09:07.171 --> 00:09:09.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creí que estabas de mi lado.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:09:09.423 --> 00:09:12.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo te pedimos unos días más, Rayla.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:13.386 --> 00:09:15.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está bien. Un día más.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:16.305 --> 00:09:17.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uno.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:17.473 --> 00:09:19.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero es en serio lo del peligro.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:19.559 --> 00:09:21.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seguiré vigilando.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:21.185 --> 00:09:23.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estén todos atentos.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:24.355 --> 00:09:25.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excepto tú.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:25.940 --> 00:09:28.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Preocúpate por despegarte del suelo.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:35.116 --> 00:09:38.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedo creer que me enseñe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una maga auténtica.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:38.744 --> 00:09:40.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo sabes que lo soy?</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:43.332 --> 00:09:44.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tranquilo. Lo soy.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:46.544 --> 00:09:48.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esto es Lunahenge.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:49.547 --> 00:09:52.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hace miles de años,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cuando Xadia era una tierra,</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:52.466 --> 00:09:57.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>los ancestros de los elfos de luna</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hacían rituales fantásticos aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:09:59.056 --> 00:10:00.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Historia viventem.</i></c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:18.826 --> 00:10:24.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Según la leyenda, usaban el poder de Nexo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para abrir un portal hacia otro plano.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:24.415 --> 00:10:27.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un mundo más allá de la vida y la muerte.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:32.632 --> 00:10:33.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está en ruinas.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:34.925 --> 00:10:35.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué pasó?</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:36.552 --> 00:10:39.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los destruyeron los druidas lunares</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:39.138 --> 00:10:41.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>cuando Xadia se dividió en dos.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:42.016 --> 00:10:46.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Le pareció más seguro</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inhabilitar este lugar mágico.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:46.937 --> 00:10:47.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Qué triste.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:48.606 --> 00:10:52.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Desde entonces, siempre ha habido</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un guardián de Nexo,</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:52.902 --> 00:10:54.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>un mago como yo,</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:55.196 --> 00:10:58.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>para evitar que los humanos lo descubran.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:59.325 --> 00:11:01.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué ocurre si lo descubren?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:11:01.827 --> 00:11:02.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tú...</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:05.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>...los matas?</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:11:07.667 --> 00:11:10.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. ¿Por qué matarlos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>si puedes volverlos locos</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:11:11.045 --> 00:11:12.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>con ilusiones disparatadas?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:11:13.214 --> 00:11:15.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Algunas son insoportables.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:15.675 --> 00:11:18.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te matarían del susto.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:18.386 --> 00:11:19.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Te interesa?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:20.304 --> 00:11:21.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mejor paso.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:21.889 --> 00:11:25.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es hora de ponerse a trabajar.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:28.437 --> 00:11:30.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Volar es algo bello y natural.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:31.315 --> 00:11:33.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eso no significa que sea fácil.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:35.695 --> 00:11:37.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puedes dejar de hacer eso.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:39.115 --> 00:11:41.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Listo, Zym? Despliega las alas.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:41.575 --> 00:11:42.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Y aletea!</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:45.246 --> 00:11:47.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Vamos, bate las alas!</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:50.292 --> 00:11:51.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No! ¿Estás bien?</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:55.589 --> 00:11:58.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Intenta una vez más. Despacio.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:58.843 --> 00:12:00.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Bate las alas!</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:12:07.852 --> 00:12:11.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No volaste, pero fue un buen comienzo.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:13:38.859 --> 00:13:42.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"¿Podemos quedarnos así aprendo magia?".</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:13:42.196 --> 00:13:45.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"¡Quiero jugar con el dragoncito!".</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:13:46.408 --> 00:13:47.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Humanos...</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:13:47.910 --> 00:13:52.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo la noble elfo se preocupa</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por mantenernos con vida.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:13:53.707 --> 00:13:56.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay algo por aquí. Lo sé.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:13:57.169 --> 00:13:58.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Algo malo.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:14:24.154 --> 00:14:28.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tú de nuevo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Guárdalo para alguien que le importe.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:14:36.667 --> 00:14:38.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya regresamos.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:14:38.252 --> 00:14:40.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y con una invitada especial.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:14:40.671 --> 00:14:43.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es mística, mágica, poderosa</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:14:43.382 --> 00:14:45.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y sabe volar.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:14:45.301 --> 00:14:47.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Denle la bienvenida a Fe-Fe.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:14:49.346 --> 00:14:51.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Lista? Muéstrale cómo se hace.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:14:55.477 --> 00:14:56.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ves? ¡Es fácil!</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:14:57.938 --> 00:14:59.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí! ¡Así!</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:15:03.569 --> 00:15:06.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ahora verás cómo se siente volar.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:15:09.909 --> 00:15:10.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Lo sientes?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:15:10.993 --> 00:15:13.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Sientes el aire bajo las alas?</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:15:16.540 --> 00:15:18.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Lo está haciendo! ¡Genial!</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:15:18.792 --> 00:15:21.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Sí, puedes hacerlo!</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:15:25.007 --> 00:15:28.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Ezran! Mataste al Príncipe Dragón.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:15:28.427 --> 00:15:30.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Qué estúpido que soy.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:15:30.804 --> 00:15:32.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No, no!</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:15:37.269 --> 00:15:38.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo siento mucho.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:15:38.687 --> 00:15:40.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No quise lastimarte.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:15:40.731 --> 00:15:41.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Estás bien?</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:15:47.321 --> 00:15:50.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si bien la energía primaria</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>está por doquier,</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:15:50.157 --> 00:15:54.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>es más leve o más fuerte</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en distintos momentos y lugares.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:15:54.912 --> 00:15:57.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El océano es más fuerte con marea alta.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:15:57.706 --> 00:16:00.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El cielo, con una tormenta.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:16:00.376 --> 00:16:03.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Y la Luna...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Cuando está llena!</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:16:03.629 --> 00:16:05.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No me interrumpas.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:16:05.547 --> 00:16:06.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero sí.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:08.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y hay más.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:16:08.092 --> 00:16:09.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay seis lugares especiales</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:16:09.927 --> 00:16:14.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>donde la magia de las energías primarias</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>es más pura y poderosa.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:16:14.723 --> 00:16:17.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un lugar así se llama Nexo.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:16:19.395 --> 00:16:22.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Este es el Nexo de Luna!</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:16:24.233 --> 00:16:26.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Refleja la Luna perfectamente.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:16:26.902 --> 00:16:30.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando hay luna llena,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>su luz inunda el lago.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:16:33.033 --> 00:16:36.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me encanta esto. Amo aprender sobre magia.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:16:37.162 --> 00:16:40.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero quiero me enseñes a hacer magia.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:16:41.834 --> 00:16:43.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Algo práctico.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:46.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Podrías enseñarme a hacer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un rayo de luna,</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:16:46.213 --> 00:16:49.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>tal vez un brillo de luna.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:16:50.050 --> 00:16:52.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los humanos no pueden hacer magia.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:16:53.137 --> 00:16:54.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero yo hice.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:16:55.264 --> 00:16:57.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Claro, con una roca primaria.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:16:57.975 --> 00:17:02.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero la rompiste</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y ahora eres un humano regular.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:17:03.439 --> 00:17:06.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mira el lado positivo: tienen dedos extra.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:17:06.442 --> 00:17:07.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los pequeños.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:17:07.609 --> 00:17:09.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo los llaman?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:17:09.194 --> 00:17:10.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡"Meñicos"!</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:17:10.446 --> 00:17:13.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conozco humanos que hacen magia.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:17:14.116 --> 00:17:17.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esa práctica no es magia.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:17:17.953 --> 00:17:19.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una atrocidad.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:17:20.539 --> 00:17:21.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puede ser.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:17:22.082 --> 00:17:24.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creía que la magia era lo mío.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:17:24.668 --> 00:17:25.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me salía bien.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:17:27.129 --> 00:17:29.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te vendría bien un poco de pastel.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:17:30.799 --> 00:17:32.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un plato de gusanos.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:17:35.179 --> 00:17:38.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres muy listo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para las ilusiones de Lujanne.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:17:38.932 --> 00:17:43.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué tal un poco de helado?</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:17:45.647 --> 00:17:46.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Son gusanos.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:17:52.529 --> 00:17:55.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fue un día entero de entrenamiento.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:56.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ya sabe volar?</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:17:56.575 --> 00:17:57.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aún no.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:17:58.285 --> 00:18:00.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hago lo mejor que puedo.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:18:00.245 --> 00:18:01.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y tú también.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:18:01.789 --> 00:18:02.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo sé.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:18:04.583 --> 00:18:07.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como sea, nos vamos mañana.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:18:07.211 --> 00:18:09.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se aproxima el peligro.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:18:09.338 --> 00:18:10.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tenemos que seguir.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:18:11.048 --> 00:18:12.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entonces descansemos.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:18:12.716 --> 00:18:14.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, yo no descansaré.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:18:14.426 --> 00:18:16.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seguiré patrullando.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:18:16.261 --> 00:18:18.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una revisión más del perímetro.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:18:24.061 --> 00:18:26.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Fue un día duro?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Algo así.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:18:26.438 --> 00:18:30.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Para nosotros también.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Mucho salto y aleteo, pero nada de vuelo.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:18:30.901 --> 00:18:34.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya lo lograremos,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aunque parezca imposible.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:18:35.114 --> 00:18:39.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Creemos en nosotros</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y no nos rendiremos, ¿verdad?</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:18:41.537 --> 00:18:42.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Sabes qué?</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:18:43.413 --> 00:18:44.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo tampoco me rendiré.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:18:56.385 --> 00:18:57.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lord Cuervo.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:18:58.846 --> 00:19:00.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oiga. Usted.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:19:00.889 --> 00:19:02.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Lord Cuervo!</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:19:02.891 --> 00:19:03.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Disculpe.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:19:03.892 --> 00:19:05.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oí que llamaba al Lord.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:19:05.894 --> 00:19:07.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No está aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:19:08.021 --> 00:19:09.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y tú quién eres?</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:19:09.565 --> 00:19:11.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soy el Maestro Cuervo.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:19:14.194 --> 00:19:17.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soy un asistente del Lord.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Acaban de ascenderme.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:19:18.866 --> 00:19:21.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te felicito. ¿Puedes enviar correo?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:19:21.577 --> 00:19:23.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, por supuesto.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:19:27.791 --> 00:19:31.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece que tienen el sello del rey.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:19:31.962 --> 00:19:32.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:19:33.088 --> 00:19:34.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno...</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:19:35.465 --> 00:19:36.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El rey está...</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:37.509 --> 00:19:38.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya sabe.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:39.469 --> 00:19:40.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedo enviarlas.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:42.764 --> 00:19:44.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entiendo tu dilema.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:44.600 --> 00:19:48.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te ascendieron,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y quieres hacer un buen trabajo.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:48.353 --> 00:19:49.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, exactamente.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:19:50.147 --> 00:19:52.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno, déjame ser...</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:19:52.691 --> 00:19:55.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>...claro, Maestro Cuervo.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:55.569 --> 00:19:59.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enviarás estas cartas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a los cuatro reinos de inmediato.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:20:00.574 --> 00:20:03.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si te niegas, tú también estarás...</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:20:04.119 --> 00:20:05.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya sabes.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:20:06.163 --> 00:20:08.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ahora que lo pienso,</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:20:08.165 --> 00:20:11.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>iré a ocuparme de estas cartas por usted.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:20:12.044 --> 00:20:13.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eso pensé.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:25.599 --> 00:20:26.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te equivocas.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:26.725 --> 00:20:27.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:20:27.643 --> 00:20:30.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué haces aquí? Es tarde.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:20:30.270 --> 00:20:31.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No me rendiré.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:20:31.772 --> 00:20:32.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum...</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:20:33.023 --> 00:20:35.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>De niño, debía aprender</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a montar a caballo,</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:20:35.943 --> 00:20:38.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>a usar espadas, tiro con arco, tácticas.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:20:38.570 --> 00:20:40.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Era pésimo en todo.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:20:40.739 --> 00:20:42.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero ¿no te rendiste?</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:20:43.283 --> 00:20:44.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y mejoraste?</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:20:44.618 --> 00:20:46.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, dejé de intentarlo.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:20:46.703 --> 00:20:48.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero probé con la magia,</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:20:48.747 --> 00:20:50.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y se sentía bien.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:20:50.582 --> 00:20:52.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Al fin me sentí bueno en algo.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:20:53.293 --> 00:20:54.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aprenderé magia.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:20:55.545 --> 00:20:56.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es quien soy.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:20:58.507 --> 00:21:00.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Admiro tu determinación.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:21:01.134 --> 00:21:04.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero aprender magia no es tu destino.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:21:04.805 --> 00:21:06.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedes hacer magia primaria</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:21:06.765 --> 00:21:10.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>porque no naciste</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>conectado a una fuente primaria.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:21:10.811 --> 00:21:13.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No entiendo. ¿"Conectado"?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:21:13.105 --> 00:21:18.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En Xadia, todas las criaturas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>nacen conectadas a una fuente primaria.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:21:20.279 --> 00:21:22.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y llevan una parte adentro,</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:21:22.614 --> 00:21:25.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>la cual llamamos arcano.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:21:25.450 --> 00:21:26.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué es un arcano?</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:21:26.952 --> 00:21:30.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es el secreto de la fuente,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>o su significado.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:21:31.498 --> 00:21:33.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿El secreto?</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:21:33.375 --> 00:21:34.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:21:34.501 --> 00:21:37.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El secreto se convierte en chispa,</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:21:37.629 --> 00:21:42.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>el destello más pequeño</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de la fuente primaria en ti,</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:21:43.010 --> 00:21:46.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero capaz de encender el mundo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con su magia.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:21:46.972 --> 00:21:50.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno, ¿cuál es el arcano de la Luna?</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:21:50.142 --> 00:21:52.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Simplemente lo sé.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:21:53.020 --> 00:21:55.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es fácil expresarlo con palabras.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:21:55.814 --> 00:21:58.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Inténtalo, por favor.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:21:58.358 --> 00:21:59.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>De acuerdo.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:21:59.818 --> 00:22:01.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El arcano de la Luna</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:22:01.862 --> 00:22:05.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>se trata de entender la relación</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>entre las apariencias</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:22:06.408 --> 00:22:07.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y la realidad.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:22:07.617 --> 00:22:10.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La mayoría cree que la realidad es cierta</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:22:11.079 --> 00:22:13.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y que las apariencias engañan.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:22:13.707 --> 00:22:16.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero los que conocen el arcano lunar</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:22:16.585 --> 00:22:21.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>comprenden que solo podemos conocer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>la apariencia misma.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:22:21.214 --> 00:22:23.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedes tocar la realidad</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:22:23.592 --> 00:22:26.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>que yace más allá del alcance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de tu percepción.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:22:29.931 --> 00:22:30.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estoy confundido.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:22:31.767 --> 00:22:32.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y es comprensible.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:22:33.518 --> 00:22:35.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Después de todo, eres humano.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:23:55.892 --> 00:23:56.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hazlo.</c.bg_transparent>

